      <div class="subfield"><strong>$0 - Record control number</strong> <em></em><div class="description">See description of this subfield in Appendix A: <em><a href="//www.loc.gov/marc/bibliographic/ecbdcntf.html">Control Subfields</a></em>.
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="subfield"><strong>$2 - Source of term</strong> <em></em><div class="description">MARC code that identifies the source of the term in subfield $a when it is from a controlled list.
         </div>
         <div class="description2">
            <div class="description">Code from: <em><a href="//www.loc.gov/standards/sourcelist/subject.html">Subject Heading and Term Source Codes</a></em>.
               					
            </div>
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="subfield"><strong>$6 - Linkage</strong> <em></em><div class="description">See description of this subfield in Appendix A: <em><a href="//www.loc.gov/marc/bibliographic/ecbdcntf.html">Control Subfields</a></em>.
         </div>
      </div>
